@startuml
title Football-Lover - Integration Diagram

component "Football-Lover Backend" as FL
cloud "Chatbot/AI Provider" as AI
cloud "Football Data API" as FDA
database "Relational DB" as DB

FL --> AI : REST JSON\nquestion + context
AI --> FL : answer text

FL --> FDA : REST JSON Pull\nschedule/scores every 15-30 min
FDA --> FL : match/team/schedule/result data

FL --> DB : persist users, matches, predictions, stats

note right of AI
  Auth: API key/bearer token server-side.
  If timeout: show chatbot unavailable.
end note

note right of FDA
  Auth: API key/bearer token server-side.
  If timeout: use cached/latest stored data if available.
end note

@enduml
